Apa awak cakap?

477
00:32:38,218 --> 00:32:39,926
Sebelum dia kerja dengan TVA?

478
00:32:40,009 --> 00:32:42,051
Ya, dia cuma manusia biasa di Bumi.

479
00:32:42,134 --> 00:32:43,259
Manusia biasa?

480
00:32:43,343 --> 00:32:44,634
Dia suka minum <i>margarita.</i>

481
00:32:45,468 --> 00:32:47,968
Mereka beritahu,
semua yang berkhidmat dengan TVA

482
00:32:48,051 --> 00:32:49,759
diciptakan oleh Penjaga Masa.

483
00:32:49,843 --> 00:32:50,884
Mengarut.

484
00:32:50,968 --> 00:32:52,968
Mereka semua varian,
sama seperti kita.

485
00:32:53,676 --> 00:32:54,926
Mereka tak tahu.

486
00:32:55,384 --> 00:32:57,110
<i>Semua penumpang dengan tiket,
laporkan diri di bahtera.</i>

487
00:32:57,134 --> 00:32:58,343
Itu pengangkutan kita.

488
00:32:58,426 --> 00:33:00,426
<i>Sepuluh minit sebelum berlepas.</i>

489
00:33:05,426 --> 00:33:06,968
<i>Panggilan terakhir.</i>

490
00:33:09,134 --> 00:33:10,509
Kita percaya satu sama lain?

491
00:33:10,593 --> 00:33:12,593
Ya dan kita boleh.

492
00:33:14,676 --> 00:33:15,676
Bagus.

493
00:33:16,218 --> 00:33:17,718
Sebab keadaan seterusnya pasti teruk.

494
00:33:18,218 --> 00:33:19,218
Benarkan kami naik!

495
00:33:19,843 --> 00:33:22,634
<i>Bawa bertenang.
Kapal ini sudah penuh.</i>

496
00:33:22,718 --> 00:33:24,676
<i>Kembali ke rumah masing-masing.</i>

497
00:33:25,634 --> 00:33:27,009
<i>Tolong berundur!</i>

498
00:33:27,093 --> 00:33:29,134
Beri kami naik!

499
00:33:29,218 --> 00:33:30,426
Beri kami masuk!

500
00:33:30,509 --> 00:33:32,509
<i>Lima minit sebelum berlepas.</i>

501
00:33:32,593 --> 00:33:34,343
Mereka semua akan mati.

502
00:33:34,426 --> 00:33:36,759
<i>Lima minit sebelum berlepas.</i>

503
00:33:36,843 --> 00:33:39,093
Kita harus masuk bahtera itu
dan pastikan ia berlepas.

504
00:33:39,176 --> 00:33:40,176
Bagaimana?

505
00:33:41,676 --> 00:33:42,759
Masuk ikut belakang.

506
00:34:00,009 --> 00:34:01,593
<i>Kembali ke rumah kamu!</i>

507
00:34:29,093 --> 00:34:30,468
- Awak okey?
- Ya.

508
00:34:44,009 --> 00:34:45,093
Ayuh!

509
00:34:54,426 --> 00:34:55,426
Ikut sini!

510
00:35:14,843 --> 00:35:15,884
Lari!

511
00:35:19,718 --> 00:35:20,718
Hati-hati!

512
00:35:21,093 --> 00:35:22,093
Biar saya halang!

513
00:35:28,759 --> 00:35:30,051
Kita masih sempat ke sana!

514
